This will make your app useful to many more people across India.

---

# Safety Rules

The AI should never:

❌ Diagnose diseases

❌ Prescribe medicines

❌ Tell users to stop treatment

❌ Promise outcomes

Instead, it should:

✅ Explain the reported values

✅ Highlight trends

✅ Encourage professional medical advice when appropriate

